data.description: **PRICE ADJUSTMENT**ASSUMABLE VA LOAN at 2.25%**Cozy 3/2/Den/Florida Room Single Family Home on 1992 Heated SqFt, located in the desirable, quiet and NO FLOOD ZONE Spanish Park neighborhood at NW Bradenton, about 10 minutes driving in between the West bound breathtaking Anna Maria Island Beach and the East bound exciting waterside Downtown Bradenton. At a short drive also the Manatee Memorial and the HCA Florida Blake Hospitals, the GT Bray Park, the Bradenton Country Golf Club, the IMG Academy, the Shopping and many delicious Restaurants; the Sarasota-Bradenton Airport is about 10 miles away. The property has been totally remodeled in *2015 including Kitchen, A/C, Electric Water Heater, Appliances (except washer & dryer), Bathrooms, Flooring, Painting. Also in *2016 New Fence,  in *2021 Backyard and Driveway paved, in *2023 New Windows (except in the Florida Room) and New Garage Opening System. The backyard features a delightful Gazebo built in 2015, a nice small water fountain, a Storage Shed and a luscious Avocado Tree! The Florida Room is under air conditioned and large enough to fit furniture and a Pool Table with the seller happy to convey to new owner! The Two Cars Garage has the Laundry Area with a convenient sink, a Side Door and an extended Workshop area or room for a Golf Cart. In case of power outage, the garage has a 220V cable that can be plugged into the dryer outlet and connected outside with a generator, in order to have the fridge, the stove, the lights and the ceiling fans worked out (A/C excluded).  Book your showing today and enjoy the SW Florida Gulf Coast lifestyle at its best.
